'''2011年温哥华史丹利杯赛后骚乱事件'''是2011年6月15日发生在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[不列颠哥伦比亚省|不列颠哥伦比亚省]][[温哥华市中心|温哥华市中心]]的一次骚乱。事件起源于2011年[[史丹利杯|史丹利杯]]冰球赛[[温哥华加人队|温哥华加人队]]在决赛第七場（亦即最後一場）賽事中输给[[波士顿棕熊队|波士顿棕熊队]]。騷亂中有最少140人受傷，當中包括9名警員，至少四人被利器刺傷。當晚共有101人被捕，其後再有16人被捕<ref name="autogenerated1994"/><ref name=NotJustAnarchists>{{cite web |url=http://www.ctvbc.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20110620/bc_riot_arrest_statistics_110620/20110620/?hub=BritishColumbiaHome |title='Anarchists' not the only rioters: Vancouver police |publisher=ctv.ca |accessdate=2011-06-20 |archive-date=2012-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404102103/http://www.ctvbc.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20110620/bc_riot_arrest_statistics_110620/20110620/?hub=BritishColumbiaHome |dead-url=no }}</ref>。類似的骚乱也曾于1994年史丹利杯決賽中温哥华加人队输给[[纽约游骑兵队|纽约游骑兵队]]之后发生。

==背景==
史丹利杯冰球決賽期間，溫哥華市政府每逢賽事進行當晚將鄰近[[羅渣士體育館|羅渣士體育館]]的一段[[佐治街_(溫哥華)|佐治街]]封閉給行人專用，並在街上設立兩個大型電視屏幕讓球迷欣賞賽事。警方在行人專用區外圍設立檢查站以控制人流，若發現有意進入行人專用區的民眾攜帶酒精飲品的話則當場將之充公。當局吸取了1994年史丹利杯騷亂的教訓，下令市中心一帶的酒舖在賽事開始前數小時關門。決賽頭六場賽事舉行時，每晚約有7萬人在行人專用區內觀賞賽事，秩序大致良好；另外[[2010年冬季奧運會|2010年冬季奧運會]]期間當局亦曾在市中心順利實施類似但較小型的安排。決賽第七場賽事舉行當日，約有10萬人湧到行人專用區，當中不少人順利繞過警方檢查站進入會場。

第七場比賽期間因球證多次對溫哥華加人不利的誤判及波士頓棕熊多次的犯規而球證卻視而不見（其中一個進球更加是波士頓棕熊球員侵犯溫哥華加人球員情況下進的），致使溫哥華加人最後慘敗給波士頓棕熊4-0。比賽之後場外的球迷情緒非常激動，因而引發今次事件。

==騷亂經過==
[[File:Riot_in_Vancouver.jpg|thumb]]
隨著賽事於晚上7時45分結束，部分在場觀眾開始將水樽和其他雜物扔往大屏幕，騷亂亦開始成形<ref name="ctvbc1"/>。有人將旗幟和球衣縱火，而加拿大郵政公司大樓門外一輛汽車亦被推翻<ref name="ctvbc1"/>。有目擊者表示一班人在賽事第一局時已高呼「去動亂吧」（"Let's go riot, let's go riot"），而這班人後來亦有份推倒第一輛汽車<ref>{{cite news |url=http://fullcomment.nationalpost.com/2011/06/18/todays-letters-who%E2%80%99s-to-blame-for-the-riots/ |title=Who's to blame for the riots? |first=Jennifer |last=Kennedy |newspaper=National Post |date=2011-06-18 |accessdate=2011-06-18 |page=A25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120710122354/http://fullcomment.nationalpost.com/2011/06/18/todays-letters-who%E2%80%99s-to-blame-for-the-riots/ |archivedate=2012-07-10 }}</ref>。第一輛汽車被推倒後，民眾跳到車上，其後將之縱火。附近另一輛汽車亦被縱火，消防員將火種撲滅後<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/vancouver-riots-timeline/article2064458/ | title=Vancouver riots timeline | publisher=The Globe and Mail | date=2011-06-16 | accessdate=2011-06-21 | location=Toronto | archive-date=2011-12-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111229170438/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/vancouver-riots-timeline/article2064458/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，該輛汽車被推翻並再度被縱火。兩輛停在附近一個停車場的溫哥華市警警車亦被縱火<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Downtown+Vancouver+rocked+Stanley+post+game+riot/4953593/story.html | title=Downtown Vancouver rocked by Stanley Cup post-game riot | newspaper=[[溫哥華太陽報|Vancouver Sun]] | date=June 16, 2011 | accessdate=June 16, 2011 | authors=Mike Hager, Andrea Woo, Adrienne Tanner | archive-date=2020-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123130226/http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Downtown+Vancouver+Rocked+Stanley+Post+Game+Riot/4953593/story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="torontoStarCarFire">{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com/sports/hockey/article/1009707--angry-canucks-fans-set-cars-ablaze-fling-bottles-after-loss?bn=1|title=Angry Canucks fans set cars ablaze, fling bottles after loss|date=June 16, 2011|work=Toronto Star|publisher=The Canadian Press|accessdate=June 16, 2011|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024105331/http://www.thestar.com/sports/hockey/article/1009707--angry-canucks-fans-set-cars-ablaze-fling-bottles-after-loss?bn=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MeisznerChaosInDowntown">{{cite web|url=http://www.globaltvbc.com/Riot+chaos+downtown+Vancouver/4953591/story.html|title=Chaos in downtown Vancouver after losing Stanley Cup|last=Meiszner|first=Peter|date=June 15, 2011|publisher=Global News|accessdate=June 16, 2011|archive-date=2011-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110619040401/http://www.globaltvbc.com/Riot%2Bchaos%2Bdowntown%2BVancouver/4953591/story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="AustinCarFlipped">{{cite web|url=http://www.theprovince.com/news/flipped+over+torched+near+Canada+Post+building/4953623/story.html?cid=megadrop_story|title=Car flipped over and torched near Canada Post building|last=Austin|first=Ian|coauthors=Cooper, Sam; Douziech, Sarah; Chan, Cheryl|date=June 15, 2011|publisher=The Province|accessdate=June 16, 2011|archive-date=2018-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180325171430/http://www.theprovince.com/news/flipped+over+torched+near+Canada+Post+building/4953623/story.html?cid=megadrop_story|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。騷亂中合共有17輛汽車被燒毀。佐治西街沿途一間銀行和數間商舖的窗戶被毀，部分商戶的貨品亦被人搶掠。騷亂人士被防暴警驅離佐治西街後轉入[[固蘭湖街|固蘭湖街]]和[[洛遜街|洛遜街]]，並進一步破壞沿途商戶。過程中一名波士頓棕熊球迷更加被溫哥華加人球迷從高處推下重傷，情況嚴重。

[[運輸聯線|運輸聯線]]旗下駛經該帶的巴士綫被逼改道或停駛，而警方則封鎖通往市中心橋樑的行車綫，以便民眾離開市中心及阻截進城人流。到了午夜，市中心內大部分民眾已被驅散。溫哥華市警在騷亂期間拘捕了101人<ref name=101arrested>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/story/2011/06/16/bc-riot-thursday.html |title=Vancouver police arrest more than 100 in riot Damage to shops and streets to cost millions |publisher=CBC News |date=2011-06-16 |accessdate=2011-06-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715091259/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/story/2011/06/16/bc-riot-thursday.html |archivedate=2011-07-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

==後續==
