===反應===
溫哥華市長[[羅品信|羅品信]]將騷亂歸咎於「一小撮滋事者」（"a small group of troublemakers"）<ref name="CBC_arrests">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/story/2011/06/16/bc-riot-thursday.html|title=Vancouver police arrest nearly 100 in riot|date=2011-06-16|work=CBC.ca|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=June 16, 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715091259/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/story/2011/06/16/bc-riot-thursday.html|archivedate=2011-07-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>。溫哥華警察局長[[朱小蓀|朱小蓀]]則指騷亂的始作俑者是假扮成球迷的「罪犯和無政府主義者」（"criminals and anarchists"）<ref name="CBC_arrests"/><ref>{{cite news |author=By the CNN Wire Staff |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/americas/06/16/canada.riots/ |title=Vancouver police blame Stanley Cup riots on anarchists CNN June 16, 2011 |publisher=Edition.cnn.com |date=2011-06-17 |accessdate=2011-06-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110617015410/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/americas/06/16/canada.riots/ |archivedate=2011-06-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但這些言論卻被部分人批評是警隊將責任卸在別人身上<ref>Law, Stephanie (June 24, 2011). [http://www.vancouversun.com/news/blame+anarchists+professor+says/4998569/story.html#ixzz1R7CrEjzY Don't blame the anarchists, UBC professor says] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/news/blame+anarchists+professor+says/4998569/story.html#ixzz1R7CrEjzY |date=20110831120805 }}. ''Vancouver Sun''. Retrieved on: 2011-07-04.</ref>。1994年史丹利杯騷亂調查報告的作者指出當局在事前計劃方面有欠妥善，如允許車主將汽車泊在大屏幕附近，又沒有移走報紙販賣箱等可用作武器的物件<ref>{{cite web |url= http://news.nationalpost.com/2011/06/18/vancouver-riot-police-made-mistakes-says-author-report-on-1994-mayhem/ |title=Vancouver Riot: Police made mistakes, says author report on 1994 mayhem|first= Sarah|last= Boesvald|work=nationalpost.com |date= 2011-06-18|accessdate=June 18, 2011}}</ref>。

===財物損失===
初步估計騷亂引致的損失約有420萬元<ref name=PowellEstimates4-5million/>，被搶掠的大型連鎖商戶包括[[哈德遜灣公司|哈德遜灣公司]]、西爾斯百貨和[[倫敦藥房|倫敦藥房]]等<ref>{{cite web |last=Hager |first=Mike |url=http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Anatomy+Riot/4962418/story.html |title=Anatomy Of A Riot |publisher=Vancouversun.com |date= |accessdate=2011-06-17 |archive-date=2016-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417100204/http://www.vancouversun.com/news/Anatomy%20Riot/4962418/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

